{"tid":1501174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足們 齊上齊落 唔好兩頭唔到岸","createTime":"2019-08-24T09:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T14:25:01.000Z","uid":60123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b121a23ce4e6303f933e065e8ed0602a5d0b7746","tid":1501174,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"次次打陣地戰都輸 人衝我縮 次次縮唔切<br />\n已經loop左好多好多次<br />\n今次仲要係人地主場玩陣地 同埋冇狗鐵走<br />\n都好難唔輸姐？附近仲要係工廠區 <br />\n居民最近都係得德福 連輿論戰都搞唔起<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔要再見到有手足俾人拉<br />\n無論係咩地點搞活動 開始之前 不如討論下點樣對自己最有利先 <br />\n包括逃走方向 逃走交通工具 若然冇得走既部署係點<br />\n<br />\n最弊既係手足們太有底線 班差佬都已經又催淚彈 又射海綿彈 橡膠子彈 用酷刑虐待被捕示威者<br />\n都仲可以同班垃圾講道理 咁搞法真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57126f180edc071cdb87f0b861a18697462d38ef","tid":1501174,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:35:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b7bda3b215abd1978cfe1e86ea8634d3fcb589","tid":1501174,"uid":60123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0131ba9d4e120d967075dad44e6714d8b8b3af4","tid":1501174,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:38:57.000Z","msg":"咁講即係叫人唔好去撚狗、佔路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圍捕梗係冇得走啦，重可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982761b22da2a032ea0ac9a4c1a88f257fdee617","tid":1501174,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:39:28.000Z","msg":"以人數黎講，我地其實贏硬。"},{"pid":"3fd6414c6185ea2aa132a0cda3b15a3ab04de3e4","tid":1501174,"uid":294783,"like":0,"dislik